\v 42 Doesn'\w t|strong="G3588"\w* \w the|strong="G2532"\w* \w Scripture|strong="G1124"\w* \w say|strong="G3004"\w* \w that|strong="G3754"\w* \w the|strong="G2532"\w* \w Christ|strong="G5547"\w* \w comes|strong="G2064"\w* \w out|strong="G1537"\w* \w of|strong="G1537"\w* \w the|strong="G2532"\w* \w seed|strong="G4690"\w* \w of|strong="G1537"\w* \w David|strong="G1138"\w* \w and|strong="G2532"\w* \w from|strong="G1537"\w* \w the|strong="G2532"\w* \w town|strong="G2968"\w* \w of|strong="G1537"\w* Bethlehem, \w where|strong="G3699"\w* \w David|strong="G1138"\w* \w was|strong="G1510"\w*?”\f + \fr 7:42 \ft I smell a rat. In verse 27 above they claimed that no one knew where the Christ was coming from; now here they say it is Beth-lehem. I suspect that there were people planted in the crowd whose job it was to create confusion, and they felt no obligation to tell the truth.\f*
\v 43 \w So|strong="G3767"\w* \w there|strong="G1722"\w* \w developed|strong="G1096"\w* \w a|strong="G1096"\w* \w division|strong="G4978"\w* \w in|strong="G1722"\w* \w the|strong="G1722"\w* \w crowd|strong="G3793"\w* \w because|strong="G1223"\w* \w of|strong="G1223"\w* \w Him|strong="G3588"\w*.
\v 44 \w Further|strong="G1909"\w*, \w some|strong="G5100"\w* \w of|strong="G1537"\w* \w them|strong="G3588"\w* \w were|strong="G3588"\w* \w wanting|strong="G2309"\w* \w to|strong="G1909"\w* \w arrest|strong="G4084"\w* \w Him|strong="G3588"\w*, \w but|strong="G1161"\w* \w no|strong="G3762"\w* \w one|strong="G5100"\w* \w laid|strong="G1911"\w* \w a|strong="G1909"\w* \w hand|strong="G5495"\w* \w on|strong="G1909"\w* \w Him|strong="G3588"\w*.
\s2 The operatives are empty-handed
\p 
\v 45 \w Then|strong="G3767"\w* \w the|strong="G2532"\w* operatives \w came|strong="G2064"\w* \w to|strong="G4314"\w* \w the|strong="G2532"\w* \w chief|strong="G2532"\w* priests \w and|strong="G2532"\w* \w Pharisees|strong="G5330"\w*, \w who|strong="G5101"\w* \w said|strong="G3004"\w* \w to|strong="G4314"\w* \w them|strong="G3588"\w*, “\nd \w Why|strong="G5101"\w*\nd* haven'\w t|strong="G3588"\w* \w you|strong="G3004"\w* \w brought|strong="G2064"\w* \w him|strong="G3588"\w*?”
