\v 25 \w So|strong="G3767"\w* \nd \w he|strong="G3754"\w*\nd* answered \w and|strong="G3767"\w* \w said|strong="G3767"\w*: “\w That|strong="G3754"\w* \w He|strong="G3754"\w* \w is|strong="G1510"\w* \w a|strong="G1510"\w* sinner, \w I|strong="G3754"\w* \w do|strong="G1492"\w* \w not|strong="G3756"\w* \w know|strong="G1492"\w*. \w One|strong="G1520"\w* \w thing|strong="G1520"\w* \w I|strong="G3754"\w* \nd \w do|strong="G1492"\w*\nd* \w know|strong="G1492"\w*, \w that|strong="G3754"\w* \w having|strong="G1492"\w* \w been|strong="G1510"\w* \w blind|strong="G5185"\w* \w I|strong="G3754"\w* \w now|strong="G3767"\w* \w see|strong="G1492"\w*!”\f + \fr 9:25 \ft Beautiful!\f*
\v 26 \w So|strong="G3767"\w* \w they|strong="G3588"\w* \w said|strong="G3004"\w* \w to|strong="G3004"\w* \w him|strong="G3588"\w* again: “\w What|strong="G5101"\w* \w did|strong="G4160"\w* \w he|strong="G3588"\w* \w do|strong="G4160"\w* \w to|strong="G3004"\w* \w you|strong="G4771"\w*? \w How|strong="G4459"\w* \w did|strong="G4160"\w* \w he|strong="G3588"\w* open \w your|strong="G4160"\w* \w eyes|strong="G3788"\w*?”\f + \fr 9:26 \ft The poor Jews are in a pickle. The fact of an extraordinary work of creation (giving sight where there never was any) won't go away, yet they refuse to acknowledge the obvious explanation. [Sort of like the ‘scientists’ of our day who refuse to acknowledge the Creator.]\f*
\v 27 \w He|strong="G2532"\w* \w answered|strong="G3004"\w* \w them|strong="G3004"\w*: “\w I|strong="G2532"\w* \w already|strong="G2235"\w* \w told|strong="G3004"\w* \w you|strong="G5210"\w* \w and|strong="G2532"\w* \w you|strong="G5210"\w* didn't listen. \w Why|strong="G5101"\w* \w do|strong="G5101"\w* \w you|strong="G5210"\w* \w want|strong="G2309"\w* \w to|strong="G2532"\w* \w hear|strong="G5101"\w* \w it|strong="G2532"\w* \w again|strong="G3825"\w*? \nd \w You|strong="G5210"\w*\nd* don't \w want|strong="G2309"\w* \w to|strong="G2532"\w* \w become|strong="G1096"\w* \w His|strong="G2532"\w* \w disciples|strong="G3101"\w* \w too|strong="G2532"\w*, \w do|strong="G5101"\w* \w you|strong="G5210"\w*?”
